  "detailed_description": "Serke is a hack and slash game where you fight against a virus invasion.<br>Use 5 different weapons to defeat your enemies and save the virtual world.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/a9d7baffe55ef4a776be7f0e89549c93.poster.avif?t=1767281397\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/a9d7baffe55ef4a776be7f0e89549c93.webm?t=1767281397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/a9d7baffe55ef4a776be7f0e89549c93.mp4?t=1767281397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Cyanea<br> Cyanea is a one-handed sword weapon with excellent mobility.<br> It is a well-balanced weapon with all abilities satisfactory.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/9a620cad6cb583245606401f7643785b.poster.avif?t=1767281397\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/9a620cad6cb583245606401f7643785b.webm?t=1767281397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/9a620cad6cb583245606401f7643785b.mp4?t=1767281397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Spinifer<br> Spinifer summons drones and turrets based on his rifle to constantly move and fight.<br> It is a weapon that can attack the enemy unilaterally from a distance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/57738087d98fcdad6c0666a70f0300b7.poster.avif?t=1767281397\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/57738087d98fcdad6c0666a70f0300b7.webm?t=1767281397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/57738087d98fcdad6c0666a70f0300b7.mp4?t=1767281397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Red clawed<br> Red clawed is a large halberd-shaped melee weapon.<br> Crush your enemies in one blow with powerful damage.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/7101418d368235d7da1e3c47bebc8ed1.poster.avif?t=1767281397\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/7101418d368235d7da1e3c47bebc8ed1.webm?t=1767281397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/7101418d368235d7da1e3c47bebc8ed1.mp4?t=1767281397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Imperator<br> Imperator is a powerful ranged weapon that uses firepower equipment.<br> Destroy enemies using high-power equipment such as shotguns, gatling, laser cannons, and grenades.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/97029cf2586c5658a4ed90d850be83a5.poster.avif?t=1767281397\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/97029cf2586c5658a4ed90d850be83a5.webm?t=1767281397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/97029cf2586c5658a4ed90d850be83a5.mp4?t=1767281397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Death stolker<br> Death stolker is a close-quarters fighting weapon.<br> Because you attack with kicks and punches, you can have a fast-paced battle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/9ceb8e6bbc12acef5772d1508fef5099.poster.avif?t=1767281397\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/9ceb8e6bbc12acef5772d1508fef5099.webm?t=1767281397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825410/extras/9ceb8e6bbc12acef5772d1508fef5099.mp4?t=1767281397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
